  "description": "<h1><strong>Accountant (9 Months)</strong></h1><p><strong>Client:</strong> Developer<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Raffles Place<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday–Friday, 8:45 AM – 6:00 PM<br /><strong>Duration:</strong> 9 months<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> Up to <strong>$4,600</strong><br /><strong></strong></p><h3><strong>Job Summary</strong></h3><h3><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></h3><p>• Ensure smooth monthly closing for subsidiaries and Jcompanies.<br />• Manage year-end audit processes and liaise with auditors.<br />• Review budget figures and tax computations for Group Reporting.<br />• Provide accounting services and reporting to  partners or investors.<br />• Prepare management reports for senior management and stakeholders.<br />• Supervise and guide 1–2 team members.<br />• Handle operational accounting queries from managers and external parties.<br />• Review management accounts prepared by overseas agents.<br />• Prepare annual tax filings for assigned entities.<br /><br />Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: biohealth@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p></p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p><p><br /></p>",
